<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>About Natyalok</title>
  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600;700&display=swap');

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      display: flex;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    .left-half {
      flex: 1;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #8B5E3C, #C9A66B);
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 3rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .right-half {
      flex: 1;
      background: #fff;
      padding: 60px 40px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .right-half h1 {
      font-size: 2.2rem;
      color: #8B5E3C;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .right-half p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
    }

    .right-half a {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 20px;
      padding: 10px 18px;
      background: #8B5E3C;
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      transition: 0.3s;
    }

    .right-half a:hover {
      background: #C9A66B;
      color: #222;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      body {
        flex-direction: column;
      }
      .left-half, .right-half {
        flex: unset;
        width: 100%;
        padding: 40px 20px;
      }
      .left-half {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="left-half">
    Natya<span style="font-family:'Mangal',sans-serif;">लोक</span>
  </div>

  <div class="right-half">
    <h1>About Natyalok</h1>
    <p>
      Natyalok is your one-stop destination for booking movie tickets online with ease. 
      Discover movies near you, select your favorite seats, and get instant confirmations. 
      We strive to make your movie experience seamless, fun, and memorable.
    </p>
    <a href="/">Back to Home</a>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
